## Build

```bash
go mod edit -replace=github.com/hookplex/hookplex/sdk=<absolute-path-to>/sdk/hookplex
go test ./...
go build -o bin/{{.ProjectName}} ./cmd/{{.ProjectName}}
```

## Claude

This scaffold wires the generated binary in router mode:

- `Stop`
- `PreToolUse`
- `UserPromptSubmit`

If you move the project, update `hooks/hooks.json` so the command points at your built binary.
